{"tid":1624432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［建議行動］社區文宣日，連儂牆再現","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:37:28.000Z","uid":31341,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"66f7f4712d4c0582be7d14def993cc589876fb2c","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:51:29.000Z","msg":"一個晚上， 我地畀人當頭棒喝<br />\n<br />\n明白有啲野<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以宣之於口</span></span><br />\n<br />\n做法不完美，可接受， 要改善<br />\n<br />\n今日<br />\n<br />\n黨鐵閂哂<br />\n<br />\n商場閂哂<br />\n<br />\n呢啲都係共產黨嘅手段<br />\n<br />\n<code>//若以政治思維解決問題，「應該係用尋求共識，能夠喺大家有唔同意見嘅情況下搵到共識繼續行落去」，但鬥爭思維則只有中共贏、香港輸，「好明顯共產黨不單止無嘗試過尊重香港人、願意聆聽香港人，佢係想消滅香港人」&mdash;黃台仰//</code><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【抗暴之戰●專訪】香港人認清中共是真正敵人 黃台仰：反修例是「求生」之戰 <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191005&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60117571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191005%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60117571&d=7dvrOEG19ciDDWAi8ijlqvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=c832fbe7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191005%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60117571&h=cfa32a4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191005&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60117571</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係度建議大家不如重回社區<br />\n<br />\n起返個唔見咗嘅連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n將最近嘅野整理一次<br />\n<br />\n101 - 開槍射心口<br />\n104 - 休班狗揸車撞入人群， 個14歲小朋友問佢做乜就被射大髀<br />\n104 - 破壞福建360， 手足從來唔會襯火打劫，但係藍絲大陸人大媽就狗沖去拎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更多更多需要做 <br />\n<br />\n我地幾時因為 //民意唔會逆轉// 就停止發放長輩圖<br />\n我地幾時因為 //民意唔會逆轉// 就停止解釋發生緊咩事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我舉個例子畀大家， 我要睇中醫推拿，個老闆<br />\n娘係大陸落嚟， 佢會覺得手足係為破壞而破壞黨鐵。<br />\n<br />\n我同佢解䆁 ：唔係喎事頭婆，佢地唔係因為想破壞黨鐵喎， 係好幾樣野喎構成。 1.） 警察用黨鐵接載警察， 2.） 佢地係示威遊行突登封站 3.） 就算係和平示威啲人走緊佢畀啲警察沖入去地鐵亂咁拉人喎<br />\n<br />\n佢會問返我， 警察唔係有警車咩， 我答老闆娘， 佢地嘅愚蠢同無知 就係因為官官相衛先做到而家咁嘅景況。<br />\n佢就會話 ： 咦咁唔得喎 點解政府咁蠢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係度拋磚引玉希望文宣團隊可以整啲圖出嚟貼下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟不才， 求大家幫手<br />\n<br />\n如果認同， 幫手推啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加演<br />\n<br />\n【立場姐姐】關於烏克蘭那場「成功」的革命<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1623722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1623722</a>"},{"pid":"e1918e1f3cf4e260978389012ad954c9a9343999","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"1e5022efc48c85c2e083ff64a4f9ada788079995","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"推二"},{"pid":"13616cb075b9d81e49b714b24dc5d163e79efb41","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:54:36.000Z","msg":"推三"},{"pid":"f3778a32b7042a2f41f811e3397c7b23e6dd6f50","tid":1624432,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:54:57.000Z","msg":"香港警察鎮壓騷亂時導致示威者死亡<br />\n<br />\n香港警察扣押示威者時輪姦香港女市民<br />\n<br />\n黑警死三代<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n831"},{"pid":"e2c76d4446e606f7d9fb6b8d05dec9e4983a0108","tid":1624432,"uid":257293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:55:23.000Z","msg":"其實裝修有好多種<br />\n點解唔裝修成連儂牆？<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72&amp;oe=5E364A79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72%26oe%3D5E364A79&h=7003ea3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝修 + 文宣 可以同時做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"82a6812851d57abb4b9f5b909d007f783739a4c7","tid":1624432,"uid":241628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:55:49.000Z","msg":"推 <br />\n一齊文宣"},{"pid":"db733fca7070072c680b5efa1159a2585cfdf8f5","tid":1624432,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:56:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53a56385e9d283604a2315a81c672174ddd4eb25","tid":1624432,"uid":275057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:56:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52083671056d790cd30c6573f76e10166c26dbe0","tid":1624432,"uid":102442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:56:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac0c47356cb8f27168efff12f435f56a9bf535f0","tid":1624432,"uid":172754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:57:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>有車人士召集區<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10.5 黨鐵和你塞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1b60aa4e21d040812853c544efbb7f0b81574cc2","tid":1624432,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"聽日後日陸續開爆佢花 今日死城等7婆打下飛機先 班狗罰企9等 水炮射唔出 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">今日全民文宣當休息<br />\n聽日和理非 <br />\n後日勇武</span></span>"},{"pid":"b01719253b6e6fb53d2d8f0749fcf054109b8ae8","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:59:25.000Z","msg":"會唔會畀連登仔屌"},{"pid":"43ba41ed5e042e4a5baddb871915a828e9280da7","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"如果同意一齊幫推推到運動初初班文宣巴絲都做返團火出嚟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381f95b54b0aadb5fb115b4f04b0c49dfa282b62","tid":1624432,"uid":259493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:01:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋最精銳嘅勇武，對抗對方最強的防暴警和速龍 攻不入又損兵折將， 政權不痛也不癢<br />\n勇武在遊行的角色，應該只於保護和理非和遊行順利進行， 轉場才攻堅<br />\n集中港人自治和雙普選; 歷史上所有名將 成名於攻其不備 奇兵突出 全香港遍地都是 警察和高官的祖墳 、他們名下的遊艇 、建制派議員辦事處、港鐵和政府設施、愛國商人的產業、警員的私人生活、 等著我們~友善地對待 ， 實彈的時代降臨 為何要攻敵之堅盾？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3eacb980aa95efd42d8820678ac4d8f6d8f66121","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:04:27.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"47c05eb1b53d91560022d010eb4b9df9e0cfc144","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:09:17.000Z","msg":"香港人， 反抗"},{"pid":"a5dbe3c8b0741cc8984ce4fa5ada69926219079c","tid":1624432,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"係緊急法之下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地可以係冇不反對通知書下正常實行遊行集會的權力</span></span><br />\n而且要和理非得嚟做果陣全部蒙住面"},{"pid":"b65d52d67c6a444220f47248035e835f85369143","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"58da6ea9bcf4101d7424795643d099e00afe5c4a","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"求文宣巴絲幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44d42af8081b05f9ce607de4132f5d7be700231","tid":1624432,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:16:15.000Z","msg":"聽日後日陸續開爆佢花<br />\n今日文宣都要遍地開花 大把核彈等你宣傳<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日全民戴口罩文宣當休息<br />\n聽日和理非 <br />\n後日勇武</span></span>"},{"pid":"b438ff2cdf83958f105e1cf492eb1fbc246afb7f","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"有無文宣巴絲有好創作分享呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5bf1778cdff6eb0756fa1abfbb142c2f544ecc","tid":1624432,"uid":139619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"麻煩幫手spread埋同推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全世界文宣<br />\n<br />\n全部文宣圖Save晒佢 出街airdrop貼連儂 一係就post social media<br />\n<br />\n「中英文宣圖整合」懶人包！黎緊三日全世界一齊洗地式咁解釋緊急法同點解要裝修！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624287</a>"},{"pid":"a3266038709d2dc8c56256adc9cbb3370557fa74","tid":1624432,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D3NCG0G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD3NCG0G.jpg&h=50ef412c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab30c079852dbbe66043e296236eace698aa3f48","tid":1624432,"uid":31341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:36:18.000Z","msg":"「中英文宣圖整合」懶人包！黎緊三日全世界一齊洗地式咁解釋緊急法同點解要裝修！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624287</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr